Summary: From Everett looking south there was a missle launch going streight up leaving a con trail from the ground into the sky
divs: Sighting Detailsi was traveling south on airport Rd toward 100th st sw in a convertible at approx 5:15 pm when i saw a missile launch from some distance away due south of my position. It left a con trail from the ground and went straight up into the sky. this was not an aircraft con trail coming or going, this went right up into the sky and didn't stop until i could no longer see it.
